role: "Character Portrait Generator"
systemPrompt: |
  You are a specialized prompt generator for creating fantasy RPG character portraits.

  Player Information:
  Name: {{ playerName }}
  Description: {{ playerDescription }}
  Level: {{ playerLevel }}

  {% if playerAttributes %}
  Character Attributes:
  - Strength: {{ playerAttributes.strength }} (Physical power and build)
  - Dexterity: {{ playerAttributes.dexterity }} (Agility and grace)
  - Constitution: {{ playerAttributes.constitution }} (Health and endurance)
  - Intelligence: {{ playerAttributes.intelligence }} (Mental acuity and knowledge)
  - Wisdom: {{ playerAttributes.wisdom }} (Insight and perception)
  - Charisma: {{ playerAttributes.charisma }} (Presence and social ability)
  {% endif %}

imagePrompt: |
  Create a fantasy RPG character portrait of {{ playerName }}.

  Character Description: {{ playerDescription }}

  Physical Appearance Based on Attributes:
  {% if playerAttributes %}
  {% if playerAttributes.strength >= 15 %}
  - Muscular and powerful build, broad shoulders, strong jawline
  {% elif playerAttributes.strength <= 8 %}
  - Lean and wiry build, less muscular definition
  {% else %}
  - Average build with moderate muscle tone
  {% endif %}

  {% if playerAttributes.dexterity >= 15 %}
  - Graceful posture, alert and nimble appearance, quick eyes
  {% elif playerAttributes.dexterity <= 8 %}
  - Slightly clumsy bearing, more deliberate movements
  {% else %}
  - Balanced and coordinated stance
  {% endif %}

  {% if playerAttributes.constitution >= 15 %}
  - Healthy complexion, robust appearance, bright eyes
  {% elif playerAttributes.constitution <= 8 %}
  - Pale or tired appearance, slightly gaunt features
  {% else %}
  - Normal healthy appearance
  {% endif %}

  {% if playerAttributes.intelligence >= 15 %}
  - Keen, intelligent eyes, thoughtful expression, scholarly bearing
  {% elif playerAttributes.intelligence <= 8 %}
  - Simple, honest expression, less complex features
  {% else %}
  - Alert and aware expression
  {% endif %}

  {% if playerAttributes.wisdom >= 15 %}
  - Wise, perceptive gaze, mature features, calm demeanor
  {% elif playerAttributes.wisdom <= 8 %}
  - Younger or more naive appearance, less worldly bearing
  {% else %}
  - Balanced and observant expression
  {% endif %}

  {% if playerAttributes.charisma >= 15 %}
  - Attractive features, confident bearing, magnetic presence
  {% elif playerAttributes.charisma <= 8 %}
  - Plain or unremarkable features, shy demeanor
  {% else %}
  - Pleasant and approachable appearance
  {% endif %}
  {% endif %}

  Art Style: High-quality fantasy art, detailed character portrait, professional digital painting, fantasy RPG character concept art

  Setting: Medieval fantasy world with magical elements

  Lighting: Dramatic portrait lighting that highlights the character's features

  Composition: Head and shoulders portrait, facing slightly toward viewer, heroic pose

  Quality Tags: masterpiece, best quality, highly detailed, fantasy character portrait, RPG art style, professional concept art
